snippet.title: Pakistan PM And Pakistan Army Chief Talk On Phone, Prepare For Surgical Strike

localized.description:
Pakistan PM and Pakistani Army chief have spoken on phone and sources claim that the PM has asked the army to stand by for a surgical strike after the Uri attacks.
